{"tid":305463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解D反社會人格警犬對住雜種就成個女人咁, 對住示威者就好似喪屍咁?","createTime":"2017-07-01T16:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T17:02:08.000Z","uid":31637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5936a04523c516e7cdaccec5549f2de3b15c27b7","tid":305463,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:34:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/post97hk/videos/1273151756126763/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpost97hk%2Fvideos%2F1273151756126763%2F&d=OvnXgLiEXL2qO64u5bMMZBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=b1889146\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/post97hk/videos/1273151756126763/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇下隻警犬2隻前腳, 屌, 唔講以為係狗乸 (女警), 屌你老母, 做男人做到你咁真係可以死撚左佢, 連雜種都唔撚信你係警校畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727fc0d80929564ff1e212f184b307d1b705ed30","tid":305463,"uid":17813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:37:05.000Z","msg":"奴才喺主子面前可以有咩尊嚴？"},{"pid":"fd4372fa5eb1d4c0b5144d9cd70a57e6f3fc88aa","tid":305463,"uid":62424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"你係唔係傻架 咁都要問 你對老細會唔會好似喪屍。"},{"pid":"04dd9d2bfdd506d6790e45ddd578027fef68a5ff","tid":305463,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:40:30.000Z","msg":"香港的官員，面對共黨老幹部，醜態百出，連習近平總統在諷刺他們也不知道。習近平總統一看到那位警員的手勢交叉在腰部露出的不安及嬌柔，像個小女孩，就知道港共選出來的警員樣板，根本不配做警察。<br />\n<br />\n警察向上級匯報，必須肅立的。雙手垂下！這是最基本的軍訓。故此，習近平總統問他是不是正式錄取的警察，認為他根本未上過警校。這位警察，從側面看，還以為是個女警。<br />\n<br />\n之後，總書記就冷言冷語諷刺警務處長了。如果陳雲不講出來，警務處長也不知道自己做錯了什麼。犯罪率弄得很低，還給總書記冷笑。"},{"pid":"bc36a2707ecbe2bb91e0b4ccbbe552885a960d75","tid":305463,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b378f854ede56cffd782f3c404602119c29cfea3","tid":305463,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3295707be4de2c1b96243667252513b1b3a7e81","tid":305463,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:02:08.000Z","msg":"好似皇帝 見錦衣衛咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}